library(magrittr)

creditos <- read_feather('../pipeline/wrangle_train/output/collapse_train_20180823_prod.feather')

creditos_train <- creditos %>% 
  filter(fechaCorte <= as.Date("2017-12-31"))

creditos_test <- creditos %>% 
  filter(fechaCorte > as.Date("2017-12-31"))

scaling <- function(x, na.rm = FALSE) (x - mean(x, na.rm = na.rm)) / sd(x, na.rm)
cols <- c('antiguedad', 'saldo_prom_decay',
                'delta_saldo_prom_decay', 'delta_saldo_sd_decay',
                'porc_puntual_prom_decay', 'porc_puntual_sd_decay')

df_train <- creditos_train[cols] %>% mutate_all(scaling)
comps <- prcomp(df_train)
evec <- comps$rotation #los renglones son loadings
evec
##                                PC1        PC2        PC3        PC4
## antiguedad              -0.4273473  0.3073070 -0.4460925  0.6709430
## saldo_prom_decay        -0.5743821  0.2323446  0.1723220 -0.1296069
## delta_saldo_prom_decay  -0.1241648 -0.3395128  0.7573839  0.5146340
## delta_saldo_sd_decay    -0.5268996  0.2611941  0.2826668 -0.4091215
## porc_puntual_prom_decay -0.3066097 -0.5852157 -0.2378139  0.1100852
## porc_puntual_sd_decay    0.3168753  0.5706222  0.2474274  0.2978091
##                                 PC5        PC6
## antiguedad              -0.09619657 -0.2540078
## saldo_prom_decay        -0.27007239  0.7047477
## delta_saldo_prom_decay  -0.12180304 -0.1264899
## delta_saldo_sd_decay     0.37441391 -0.5164182
## porc_puntual_prom_decay  0.64943721  0.2703152
## porc_puntual_sd_decay    0.58396634  0.2881892
eval <- comps$sdev
print(eval)
## [1] 1.4561268 1.2610311 1.0616242 0.6925680 0.6259352 0.5394480
summary(comps)
## Importance of components:
##                           PC1    PC2    PC3     PC4    PC5    PC6
## Standard deviation     1.4561 1.2610 1.0616 0.69257 0.6259 0.5394
## Proportion of Variance 0.3534 0.2650 0.1878 0.07994 0.0653 0.0485
## Cumulative Proportion  0.3534 0.6184 0.8063 0.88620 0.9515 1.0000
df_test <- creditos_test[cols] %>% mutate_all(scaling)
rot_df_test <- as.matrix(df_test) %*% evec
rot_df_test <- as.data.frame(rot_df_test)
rot_df_test$label_impuntual_2 <- creditos_test$label_impuntual_2
rot_df_test %>% 
  sample_n(200) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x=PC1, y=PC2, colour=label_impuntual_2)) + 
  geom_point()

library(ggrepel)

evec %>% 
  as.data.frame() %>%
  rownames_to_column() %>% 
  as_tibble() %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x=PC1,y=PC2,label=rowname)) + 
  geom_point() + 
  geom_label_repel()
